  <rte>
    <name>Grange and Watendlath from Rosthwaite</name>
    <desc>Combining the delights of Borrowdale with the rural charm of Watendlath, this Lake District walk offers some wonderful Lakeland views and relatively easy walking. Route finding is generally easy although there is a steady ascent from Lodore up to Watendlath.</desc>
	<author>Copyright Walking Britain</author>
	<url>www.walkingbritain.co.uk/walk-1693-description</url>
	<urlname>Walk - Grange and Watendlath from Rosthwaite</urlname>
      
